<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ أَيْضاً:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١ - أَلا رُبَّ ذِي نُصْحٍ وَقَدْ تَسْتَغِشُّهُ ... وَمِنْ جَاهِدٍ فِي الْغِشِّ يُحْسَبُ نَاصِحَا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٩٤٨)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ أَيْضاً:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>١ - رَأَيْتُكَ تُقْصِي مَنْ يَوَدُّكَ قَلْبُهُ ... وَتُدْنِي الَّذِي يَطْوِي الأَذَى فِي الْجَوَانِحِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٢ - وَقَدْ يَسْتَغِشُّ الْمَرءُ مَنْ لا يَغُشُّهُ ... وَيَأْمَنُ بِالْغَيْبِ امْرءًا غَيْرَ نَاصِحِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٩٤٩)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ أَيْضاً:</span> <span class="c2">(الرمل)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>١ - رُبَّ مَنْ أَغْتَشُّهُ يَنْصَحُنِي ... وَأَخِي نُصْحٍ بِغَيْبٍ قَدْ يَخُونْ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٩٥٠)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ عَبْدُ الرَّحْمنِ بْنُ حَسَّانَ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>١ - وَرُبَّ امْرِئٍ تَعْتَدُّهُ لكَ نَاصِحاً ... يُوَلِّيكَ عَمْداً سَهْمَهُ إِذْ يُفَوّقُ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>٢ - وَمُطَّرَحٍ لا تَأْمُلُ الدَّهْرَ نَفْعَه ... تُصَادِفُ مِنْهُ مَصْدَقاً حِينَ تُرْهَقُ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>٣ - وَقَدْ تَأمَنُ الشَّرَّ الَّذِي هُوَ حاضِرٌ ... وَيُهْدَى لَكَ الشَّرُّ الْبَعِيدُ فَيَطْرُقُ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٩٥١)</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ الْحُصَيْنُ بْنُ الْمُنْذِرِ الرَّقَاشِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>